extends layout.pug
block introduction
  //  Introduction
  section#introduction.wrapper
    .inner
      .split
        .content
          header
            h2 Cold Storage Simplified
          p Cold storage solutions prevent unauthorized network access to your digital assets. Removing the constant threat that came with an Internet connection also meant removing convenience. 
          p Our Biometric Wallet is changing that. The D'CENT Biometric Wallet is the world's first über convenient cold storage solution.
          p Our easy-to-use hardware wallets are never directly exposed to the Internet. D’CENT Wallets use certified EAL5+ Secure Element (SE) technology to securely store sensitive information and mitigate network threats. All operations in D’CENT Wallets are safely executed in our Secure OS.
        .box.alt
          .row#wallet-display
            .col-2
            .col-8
              span.image.fit#dcent-biometric-wallet-diplay-image
                img(src='images/iotrust-biometric-wallet-displayed-564x840px.png' alt='Biometric Wallet')
            .col-2
      .box.alt
        .row#dcent-biometric-wallet-features
          .col-1.col-2-medium.col-3-xsmall
            span.icon.fa-stack.fa-2x
              i.far.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fas.fa-award.fa-stack-1x
          .col-2.col-4-medium.col-9-xsmall
            .row
              sub EAL5+ Certified
            .row
              sub Secure Element
          .col-1.col-2-medium.col-3-xsmall
            span.icon.fa-stack.fa-2x
              i.far.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fas.fa-fingerprint.fa-stack-1x
          .col-2.col-4-medium.col-9-xsmall
            .row
              sub Biometric
            .row
              sub Authentication
          .col-1.col-2-medium.col-3-xsmall
            span.icon.fa-stack.fa-2x
              i.far.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fab.fa-bluetooth-b.fa-stack-1x
          .col-2.col-4-medium.col-9-xsmall
            .row
              sub Bluetooth
            .row
              sub Low Energy
          .col-1.col-2-medium.col-3-xsmall
            span.icon.fa-stack.fa-2x
              i.far.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fas.fa-eye.fa-stack-1x
          .col-2.col-4-medium.col-9-xsmall
            .row
              sub OLED
            .row
              sub Display
      p The D'CENT Biometric Wallet turns the initiation of a transaction into a trivial flick of an authenticated finger.
      ul.actions
        li
          a.button.next(href='https://dcentwallet.com/overview/specification.html') Learn More
block download
  //  Download
  section#download.wrapper.style2
    .inner
      .split
        .content
          header
            h2 Mobile Apps
          p We've focused on developing iOS and Android mobile apps for those that want to securely manage their digital assets with our hardware wallets.
          p Download the app for your mobile device. Use it to securely and conveniently manage your digital assets with D'CENT Wallets.
          ul.actions.fit
            li
              a.button.fab.fa-google-play.fit(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kr.iotrust.dcent.wallet') Android App
            li
              a.button.fab.fa-apple.fit(href='https://itunes.apple.com/kr/app/dcent-hardware-wallet/id1447206611?mt=8') iOS App
        a(href='#').image.fit
          img(src='images/dcent-wallet-mobile-app-display.png' style='padding-top:4rem' alt)
block team
  //  Team
  section#team.wrapper
    .inner
      a(href='https://medium.com/iotrust/introducing-io-trust-16c536c6a65c').image.main#iotrust-team
        img(src='images/iotrust-team.png' alt)
      h2#team-heading IoTrust
      p IoTrust Company (Korea) Limited was founded in January 2017. We are venture capital funded. Jiran Security and Korea Investment Partners, Korea’s premier venture capital group, identified the potential for growth in the market for hardware wallets and were willing to place their bets on us.
      p We are security specialists. Our team boasts an average of 17+ years of relevant experience in the security domain.
      p Our security experts leverage highly-specialized knowledge of Secure Element (SE) and Trusted Execution Environment (TEE) technologies to make hardware wallets easier to use.
